cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.DS 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with the segmentation of hyperspectral satellite imagery. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category as it discusses the validation of segmentation algorithms. Additionally, it involves image retrieval (cs.IR) as it discusses the generation of benchmarks for segmentation. Multimedia (cs.MM) is another possible sub-category as it deals with satellite imagery. Finally, data structures (cs.DS) may also be relevant as the paper discusses the partitioning of training and test data.
